-- MOVES-Exotix Partners hires Fabrizio Ferrero from Morgan Stanley
-- 
-- Mon Sep 29, 2014 09:18AM EDT
-- None



Sept 29 (Reuters) - Exotix Partners, an investment bank specializing in frontier markets, said it appointed Fabrizio Ferrero head of investment banking for its EMEA region.

Ferrero, who will join Exotix's management committee, was managing director at Morgan Stanley's EMEA financial institutions group.